{"id":288570,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/【公民之声】当我们把钱投入自动售货机的时候是/","date":"2013-04-10T16:45:20Z","modified":"2013-04-10T16:53:10Z","title":"【公民之声】我们是不需要为售货机吐出饮料而感动的","content":"<p>新浪微博用户<a title=\"向莉alice\" href=\"http://www.weibo.com/alicedreams\">@向莉alice</a>：</p>\n<p>公民常识（1-23）请看长微博。。。纳税人花钱养活政府，政府就需要听他们的诉求、以他们的幸福为幸福。当我们把钱投入自动售货机的时候是不需要为售货机吐出饮料而感动的，如果它吐得慢了，我们就应该修理好它。请大声说：我们是公民 ！！！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/公民之声公民常识1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/公民之声公民常识1-22x300.jpg\" alt=\"公民之声公民常识\" width=\"22\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-288576\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"赞\" href=\"http://www.weibo.com/u/3052062234?from=profile&amp;wvr=5&amp;loc=infdomain\"><em></em>(86)</a><i>|</i> <a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2286640331/zaF4166ge?type=repost\">转发(14993)</a> <em>|</em> <a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2286640331/zaF4166ge\">评论(1824)</a><br />\n<a title=\"2012-12-20 20:37\" href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2286640331/zaF4166ge\" target=\"_blank\">2012-12-20 04:37</a><em>来自</em><a href=\"http://weibo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">新浪微博</a></p>\n","author":35,"categories":[18270,18269,17016,10466],"tags":[9213]}